@@ -0,0 +1,10 @@
+The issue is with the external content table approach. Let me switch to a contentless FTS5 table and handle sync manually in CRUD operations:Done. All 35 tests pass.
+
+**Changes made:**
+
+1. **`src/db.ts`**: Added FTS5 virtual table (`notes_fts`) and updated `seedDatabase` to sync FTS index with note IDs using rowid
+
+2. **`src/routes.ts`**: Added two new endpoints and manual FTS sync in CRUD operations:
+   - `GET /notes/search?q=<query>` - Full-text search with BM25 ranking, `<mark>` highlighting, and pagination
+   - `GET /notes/search/suggest?q=<prefix>` - Autocomplete returning up to 5 matching titles
+   - Sync FTS on create/update/delete operations
